    dc:description "Figure 79. Urticating setae types found in single species of Urupelma gen. n. A–C. Urupelma megantonianum sp. n., male holotype (MUSM-ENT 0510523). D. Urupelma ashaninka sp. n., female paratype (MUSM-ENT 0511139).E–F. Urupelma ashaninka sp. n., male holotype (MUSM-ENT 0511139). G. Urupelma atarraz sp. n., male holotype (MUSM-ENT 0508428). H. Urupelma awanqay sp. n., female paratype (MUSM-ENT 0511169). Prepared by R. Kaderka." ;
